creator: OR Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Feel the freedom of bluetooth!

This remote control app puts you in charge of your Organic Response enabled lighting installation. A wide range of settings is available using just the bluetooth functionality on your device. Utilise these configuration and optimisation settings offered by Organic Response Express to help significantly reduce your energy costs whilst simultaneously improving the lighting quality for building occupants.

Organic Response, a Fagerhult company, services the Group’s global network of companies. The business combines world-class research and development in IoT solutions, intimate customer knowledge and global reach to deliver the integrated smart lighting solutions of the future, today.

Requires Organic Response sensor nodes to have firmware 4.2 (Apr 2021) or later installed.
descriptionShort: Control Organic Response enabled lighting using just your bluetooth device.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Initial release of the OR Express app.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Organic Response January 2022.

What’s new:
- Added support for Advanced Driver Metrics queries, available on a new page in the app. Must be used with compatible Organic Response Sensor Nodes and DALI-2 drivers.
- Improvements to the way that commands and queries are sent to Organic Response Sensor Nodes.
- Reduced the number of clicks required to see critical information about a selected Organic Response Sensor Node.
